EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO MOTOR AND OTHER VEHICLES -- PUPIL TRANSPORTATION
VEHICLES
***
1 This act would amend the definitions of a “pupil transportation vehicle” to a vehicle
2 constructed to seat not more than ten (10) passengers plus the operator, rather than the existing limit
3 of eight (8) passengers.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
